lead_paragraph: India's batsmen would have to watch out for variable bounce more than prodigious turn on a Rajkot wicket which was at its best for batting on the first two days, England centurion Moeen Ali said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Moeen Warns India Batsmen Against Variable Bounce
